nodes.text: This cantina was located in the Galactic Republic's capital city, the Galactic City on Coruscant.
This cantina contained a central bar, two special rooms where gusts could be alone as well as multiple Twi'lek dancers and a band composed of three Bith and an Ithorian.
Around the year 21 BBY, bounty hunters Chata Hyoki and Robonino came to this cantina to talk to Count Dooku about an assassination attempt on senator Padmé Amidala.
